OL,3,CJersey's former Prison Governor says
OL,4,Cthe working culture left her 'with
OL,5,Canxiety'
OL,7,FJersey's former Prison Governor has
OL,8,Ftold ITV News how a lack of support
OL,9,Ffrom her managers and HR within the
OL,10,Fgovernment, left her with chronic
OL,11,Fanxiety.
OL,13,FIn an exclusive interview with ITV
OL,14,FNews, Susie Richardson highlights what
OL,15,Fshe feels needs to change within the
OL,16,Fcivil service to improve the working
OL,17,Fenvironment, warning her successor to
OL,18,F"be careful".
