OL,7,FSusie Richardson became La Moye's
OL,8,FGovernor in 2021 after her predecessor
OL,9,FNick Cameron resigned in 2020 after
OL,10,Fclashing with the Head of Home
OL,11,FAffairs, Julien Blazeby, over a lack
OL,12,Fof PPE for the prison.
OL,14,FDuring her time, she saved the prison
OL,15,F#500,000 a year by working more
OL,16,Fclosely with other government
OL,17,Fdepartments.
