OL,7,FShe also changed the prison's approach
OL,8,Fto rehabilitation, explaining: "I had
OL,9,Fthe amazing opportunity of taking a
OL,10,Fgroup of prison officers and probation
OL,11,Fofficers to Norway to look at what
OL,12,F'good' looks like.
OL,14,F"I didn't want rehabilitation to be
OL,15,Fseen as a soft thing. (I wanted) to
OL,16,Fdemonstrate how good it feels when
OL,17,Fyou're rehabilitative and making life-
OL,18,Fchanging opportunities for people and
OL,19,Fthat was really significant and
OL,20,Feffective."
