OL,7,FHowever, Susie resigned in July ending
OL,8,F20 years of service in His Majesty's
OL,9,FPrisons saying she felt unsupported.
OL,11,FShe explains: "Some of the processes,
OL,12,Fthat are set up to support services
OL,13,Fwithin government I found really
OL,14,Ffrustrating and tricky to work with.
OL,15,FAnd I've felt much better able to
OL,16,Fshare those frustrations since I
OL,17,Fresigned.
