OL,3,CJersey's former Prison Governor says
OL,4,Cthe working culture left her 'with
OL,5,Canxiety'
OL,7,F"When I arrived, I was staggered by
OL,8,Fthe number of things that were
OL,9,Funresolved - there was a senior
OL,10,Fmanager suspended and unresolved,
OL,11,Fthere was a prison officer suspended,
OL,12,Fthere were grievances that hadn't been
OL,13,Fdealt with and a number of
OL,14,Fdisciplinary hearings.
OL,16,F"Some of them were years old and I
OL,17,Fjust didn't feel there was an appetite
OL,18,Fto hear that. I felt I'd gone as far
OL,19,Fas I could within the organisation and
OL,20,Fthat it was time to leave."
