OL,5,Canxiety'
OL,7,FSusie also reveals how the culture and
OL,8,Fenvironment affected her
OL,9,Fpsychologically.
OL,11,FShe explains: "For the first time
OL,12,Fever, I suffered from anxiety - 17
OL,13,Fyears working in big ugly Victorian
OL,14,Fprisons in the UK I never did.
OL,16,F"I felt anxious because it didn't
OL,17,Falways feel safe to be open and
OL,18,Ftransparent about things - it didn't
OL,19,Ffeel like that was the culture.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/13
