OL,3,CJersey's former Prison Governor says
OL,4,Cthe working culture left her 'with
OL,5,Canxiety'
OL,7,F"People kept warning me to be cautious
OL,8,Fand I don't understand where that fear
OL,9,Fcomes from but I see it in a lot of
OL,10,Fpeople - not having the ability to do
OL,11,Fthe right thing."
OL,13,FSusie believes there must be change,
OL,14,Fexplaining: "I would love more
OL,15,Fopenness and transparency and that
OL,16,Frequires the fear to go, not just in
OL,17,Fgovernment but the wider culture of
OL,18,Fthe island - to accept that sometimes
OL,19,Fthere are problems and sometimes
OL,20,Fproblems have to come out and get
OL,21,Fworse before they get better.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/13
