OL,3,CJersey's former Prison Governor says
OL,4,Cthe working culture left her 'with
OL,5,Canxiety'
OL,7,F"Despite this beautiful well-resourced
OL,8,Fisland, it feels like there's this
OL,9,Ffunny dark cloud over it that I think
OL,10,Fis described as the 'Jersey way'.
OL,12,F"I'd love us to blow that apart, for
OL,13,Fit to feel like a psychologically safe
OL,14,Fplace to be, where people can make
OL,15,Fmistakes and we support them to get
OL,16,Fback on their feet."
