OL,7,FSusie warned the next Prison Governor
OL,8,Fto "be careful", adding: "I was told
OL,9,Fthat the Government of Jersey likes
OL,10,Fharmony and that that's the most
OL,11,Fimportant thing, for example tussling
OL,12,Fwith difficult stuff isn't necessarily
OL,13,Fencouraged.
OL,15,F"Prison Governors are my network, I
OL,16,Fknow them all and if I'm asked 'Can
OL,17,Fyou recommend working for the
OL,18,FGovernment of Jersey?' I would say if
OL,19,FI could I would still be in it.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
