OL,7,FIn response, Deputy Malcolm Ferey,
OL,8,FVice-Chair of the States Employment
OL,9,FBoard says: "My understanding is that
OL,10,Fthere were no suspensions in place at
OL,11,Fthe time when Susie arrived in her new
OL,12,Frole as Prison Governor.
OL,14,F"We strive, as an organisation, to
OL,15,Fensure that all public servants are
OL,16,Ftreated fairly and with respect,
OL,17,Fensuring that everyone has a
OL,18,Fmeaningful voice on matters that
OL,19,Faffect them, in addition to their
OL,20,Fstatutory rights and protections.
